        "\n",
        "-   ğŸ—‚ï¸ Provides [comprehensive project management](https://github.com/astral-sh/uv?tab=readme-ov-file#projects), with a [universal lockfile](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/concepts/projects/layout#the-lockfile).\n",
